adHeader: Get paid to get your teeth cleaned! *must qualify*
adDetails: If you are between the ages of 21-35 and haven't had your teeth cleaned in 4 or more years, you could possibly qualify to be paid up to $200 to get your teeth cleaned!!! Seriously, who doesn't want to be PAID cash to get their teeth cleaned?!? This is not spam! Email for details and an appointment to see if your mouth qualifies!
